E-01
E-02 PLAN PUBLICATION DATE IS LOGICAL ERROR
E-03
E-04 INPUT PART NO
E-05 THERE IS NOT PART NO INPUT INTO IN PART INFORMATION M/F
E-06 THERE ISN'T IT IN PT PLAN PUBLIC MANAGEMENT M/F
E-07 IT IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-08 THERE IS DATA
E-09
E-10 THIS PART IS NOT ASJ PART
